TEXT.TITLE: PRIME MEDICAL <PMSI> SAYS MERGER TALKS END
TEXT.BODY: Prime Medical Services Inc said merger talks with National HMO Corp <NHMO> have been terminated. Prime gave no reason for the termination of the talks with National HMO. Reuter
